            <h2 class="font-kanit font-semibold text-3xl">
                Scholarships for Undergraduate Student
            </h2>
            <p>
                Not only that scholarships for graduate students would provide
                more opportunities for students to pursue higher level study in
                mathematics and computer science, we also provide additional
                academic experiences such as teaching experience and academic
                presentation experience.
            </p>

            <Table>
                <TableHeader>
                    <TableRow>
                        <TableHead>Scholarships</TableHead>
                        <TableHead>Tuition Fee</TableHead>
                        <TableHead>Allowance</TableHead>
